Don't make these mistakes 👇🏻

🚩 Bad Lighting

Lighting can make or break your video! Dull lighting hides details and makes your content look unprofessional. Try filming near a window or use a small ring light. Good lighting makes your video look clean and professional!

⸻

🚩 Shaky Camera
Shaky videos can look messy and low-effort. Use a tripod to keep your phone steady — you can find great ones on Amazon.

⸻

🚩 Not Engaging Enough
People scroll fast! Keep your videos short and interesting. Add B-roll clips, cut out long pauses, and make sure every second keeps viewers watching.

⸻

🚩 Text Too Close to Edges
If your text or important parts are too close to the edge, Instagram might cut them off with captions or buttons. Keep your content in the center area to make sure it’s always visible.

⸻

✨ Fixing these small mistakes can make your videos look 10x better — and brands will love that!
